---------------------------------Read Me---------------------------------------
The application serves as a card manager, it lets users store cards by type.

Cards are stored into 7 types:  1. reward card
                                2. balance card
                                3. membership card
                                4. bank card
                                5. ID card
                                6. Government ID card
                                7. Other

User can choose to:             1. add a card
                                2. remove a card
                                3. view all cards
                                4. view cards by type
                                5. search for a card
                                6. back up all card information to a txt file

The application handles most edge cases and user input errors. Exceptions are
designed to be raised when invalid inputs are passed from users.
Note: The application allows empty user inputs except for card names.